ose-li:mb-3 prose-li:ps-1 prose-li:ms-1 w-full max-w-none"><div class="thinking-container mb-3"><div class="flex flex-col"><button class="flex flex-row items-center text-secondary gap-1 relative cursor-pointer group/notes"><div class="transition-opacity duration-200 group-hover/notes:opacity-0"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-[2] "><path d="M19 9C19 12.866 15.866 17 12 17C8.13398 17 4.99997 12.866 4.99997 9C4.99997 5.13401 8.13398 3 12 3C15.866 3 19 5.13401 19 9Z" class="fill-yellow-100 dark:fill-yellow-300 origin-center transition-[transform,opacity] duration-100 scale-0 opacity-0"></path><path d="M15 16.1378L14.487 15.2794L14 15.5705V16.1378H15ZM8.99997 16.1378H9.99997V15.5705L9.51293 15.2794L8.99997 16.1378ZM18 9C18 11.4496 16.5421 14.0513 14.487 15.2794L15.5129 16.9963C18.1877 15.3979 20 12.1352 20 9H18ZM12 4C13.7598 4 15.2728 4.48657 16.3238 5.33011C17.3509 6.15455 18 7.36618 18 9H20C20 6.76783 19.082 4.97946 17.5757 3.77039C16.0931 2.58044 14.1061 2 12 2V4ZM5.99997 9C5.99997 7.36618 6.64903 6.15455 7.67617 5.33011C8.72714 4.48657 10.2401 4 12 4V2C9.89382 2 7.90681 2.58044 6.42427 3.77039C4.91791 4.97946 3.99997 6.76783 3.99997 9H5.99997ZM9.51293 15.2794C7.4578 14.0513 5.99997 11.4496 5.99997 9H3.99997C3.99997 12.1352 5.81225 15.3979 8.48701 16.9963L9.51293 15.2794ZM9.99997 19.5001V16.1378H7.99997V19.5001H9.99997ZM10.5 20.0001C10.2238 20.0001 9.99997 19.7763 9.99997 19.5001H7.99997C7.99997 20.8808 9.11926 22.0001 10.5 22.0001V20.0001ZM13.5 20.0001H10.5V22.0001H13.5V20.0001ZM14 19.5001C14 19.7763 13.7761 20.0001 13.5 20.0001V22.0001C14.8807 22.0001 16 20.8808 16 19.5001H14ZM14 16.1378V19.5001H16V16.1378H14Z" fill="currentColor"></path><path d="M9 16.0001H15" stroke="currentColor"></path><path d="M12 16V12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="square"></path><g><path d="M20 7L19 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" class="transition-[transform,opacity] duration-100 ease-in-out translate-x-0 translate-y-0 opacity-0"></path><path d="M20 9L19 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" class="transition-[transform,opacity] duration-100 ease-in-out translate-x-0 translate-y-0 opacity-0"></path><path d="M4 7L5 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" class="transition-[transform,opacity] duration-100 ease-in-out translate-x-0 translate-y-0 opacity-0"></path><path d="M4 9L5 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" class="transition-[transform,opacity] duration-100 ease-in-out translate-x-0 translate-y-0 opacity-0"></path></g></svg></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center opacity-0 group-hover/notes:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-panel-left-open rotate-180"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"></rect><path d="M9 3v18"></path><path d="m14 9 3 3-3 3"></path></svg></div></div><span>Thought for 5s</span></button></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="relative response-content-markdown markdown [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:text-current [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose):hover]:text-primary [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose):hover]:decoration-primary [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:underline [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:decoration-primary/30 [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:underline-offset-2 [&amp;&gt;:first-child:not(.not-prose)]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;:last-child:not(.not-prose)]:mb-0"><p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong class="font-semibold">Tee time check, Will!</strong> ⛳️ We're building that <strong class="font-semibold">golf social network</strong> where you and the crew can post rounds, drop scores, banter in comments, climb leaderboards, and lock in with username/password accounts. Solid foundation from our earlier chats.</p>
<h3 dir="auto" class="font-semibold text-xl max-md:font-display max-md:text-[19px] max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:tracking-[0px] max-md:mb-3 max-md:mt-3">What I need from you next to keep driving this forward:</h3>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><strong class="font-semibold">Core Features Priority</strong> – Rank these (or add new ones):<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">User accounts (register/login with username/password, maybe email?)</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Post a round: course name, date, scores per hole (or total + handicap), optional photos/notes</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Feed to view friends' rounds</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Comments on posts/rounds</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Leaderboards (e.g., best score this month, handicap trends, course-specific)</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Friend connections or private groups</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Profile with stats/history</li>
</ul></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><strong class="font-semibold">Tech &amp; Scope Preferences</strong>:<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Simple static/HTML+JS prototype first (easy to run locally)?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Full web app with database (Node/Python backend, SQLite/Postgres)?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Mobile-friendly only, or desktop too?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Any hosting preference (free tiers like Render, Vercel, Netlify)?</li>
</ul></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><strong class="font-semibold">Design &amp; Golf Vibes</strong>:<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Green fairway theme? Minimal clean look? Dark mode for night rounds?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Specific pages or flows you want mocked up (e.g., scorecard entry form, leaderboard table)?</li>
</ul></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><strong class="font-semibold">Extra Details</strong>:<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Any existing courses list or handicaps to seed?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Privacy: friends-only vs public?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Future stretch goals (live scoring, swing video uploads, GHIN integration)?</li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Drop whatever you've got—ranked list, sketches, or "just make a basic version with X first"—and I'll start coding files right here in the workspace. We can iterate hole-by-hole like a solid practice round.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">What's your next shot? Let's get this birdie! 🚀</p></div></div><section class="inline-media-container flex flex-col gap-1 clear-both"></section></div><div class="order-first sticky hidden @md/mainview:block top-11 h-0 opacity-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100 -ml-[36px] @lg/mainview:-ml-[40px] -left-[26px]"><div class="min-h-7 py-4 flex flex-col gap-0.5"></div></div><div class="action-buttons h-8 mt-0.5 mb-2 flex flex-row flex-wrap w-full justify-between print:hidden"><div class="flex items-center gap-[2px] w-max rounded-lg text-xs px-2 start-0 @md/chat:start-3 -ml-4" style="bottom: 0px;"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium leading-[normal] cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-colors duration-100 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 select-none text-fg-secondary hover:text-fg-primary hover:bg-button-ghost-hover disabled:hover:text-fg-secondary disabled:hover:bg-transparent [&amp;_svg]:hover:text-fg-primary h-8 w-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100 [.last-response_&amp;]:opacity-100 disabled:opacity-0 group-focus-within:disabled:opacity-60 group-hover:disabled:opacity-60 [.last-response_&amp;]:disabled:opacity-60" type="button" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><div style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"><div class="[&amp;&gt;svg_*]:stroke-current" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); content-visibility: visible;"><defs><clippath id="__lottie_element_93"><rect width="24" height="24" x="0" y="0"></rect></clippath><g 