re-wrap;"><strong class="font-semibold">Locked and loaded, Will!</strong> ⛳️</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">I’ve expanded the course list nationwide using Google-sourced top/famous USA courses (icons like Pebble Beach, Pine Valley, Augusta National, Torrey Pines, and many more from across states).</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">It’s still lightweight and free — no bloat, just a smart dropdown with ~80+ real courses for now (we can add more later without slowing things down).</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong class="font-semibold">Reload <button class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono cursor-pointer bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300" type="button">index.html</button></strong> to see the updated Post Round form. Searchable/selectable courses from coast to coast!</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">What’s next on the card?</p>
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">More courses?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Hole-by-hole scoring?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Leaderboard improvements?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Free deploy steps?</li>
</ul>
