" stroke-linecap="round" class="transition-[transform,opacity] duration-100 ease-in-out translate-x-0 translate-y-0 opacity-0"></path><path d="M20 9L19 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" class="transition-[transform,opacity] duration-100 ease-in-out translate-x-0 translate-y-0 opacity-0"></path><path d="M4 7L5 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" class="transition-[transform,opacity] duration-100 ease-in-out translate-x-0 translate-y-0 opacity-0"></path><path d="M4 9L5 8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" class="transition-[transform,opacity] duration-100 ease-in-out translate-x-0 translate-y-0 opacity-0"></path></g></svg></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center opacity-0 group-hover/notes:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200"><div class="flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-panel-left-open rotate-180"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"></rect><path d="M9 3v18"></path><path d="m14 9 3 3-3 3"></path></svg></div></div><span>Thought for 3s</span></button></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="relative response-content-markdown markdown [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:text-current [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose):hover]:text-primary [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose):hover]:decoration-primary [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:underline [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:decoration-primary/30 [&amp;_a:not(.not-prose)]:underline-offset-2 [&amp;&gt;:first-child:not(.not-prose)]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;:last-child:not(.not-prose)]:mb-0"><p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong class="font-semibold">Perfect drive, Will — we’re going fully online for free!</strong> ⛳️</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">No laptop required 24/7. The <strong class="font-semibold">Fairway Friends</strong> site can live on the internet forever using <strong class="font-semibold">completely free hosting</strong>.</p>
<h3 dir="auto" class="font-semibold text-xl max-md:font-display max-md:text-[19px] max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:tracking-[0px] max-md:mb-3 max-md:mt-3">Best Free Options (Zero Cost):</h3>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><strong class="font-semibold">GitHub Pages</strong> (easiest &amp; most reliable for this) — Static sites run forever for free.</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><strong class="font-semibold">Netlify</strong> or <strong class="font-semibold">Vercel</strong> (also excellent free tiers).</li>
</ol>
<h3 dir="auto" class="font-semibold text-xl max-md:font-display max-md:text-[19px] max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:tracking-[0px] max-md:mb-3 max-md:mt-3">Quick Steps to Get It Live:</h3>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><strong class="font-semibold">Create a free GitHub account</strong> (if you don’t have one).</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Create a new repository named <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300">fairway-friends</span> (or similar).</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Upload the three files (<button class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono cursor-pointer bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300" type="button">index.html</button>, <button class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono cursor-pointer bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300" type="button">styles.css</button>, <button class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono cursor-pointer bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300" type="button">script.js</button>).</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Go to Settings → Pages → Source = Deploy from main branch.</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Your site will be live at: <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300">https://yourusername.github.io/fairway-friends</span></li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">I can help you optimize the files right now for perfect GitHub Pages deployment (add a manifest, better mobile support, etc.).</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Want me to:</p>
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Update the code for immediate deployment readiness?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Give exact step-by-step instructions with screenshots in mind?</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Add any final touches before you push it live?</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Just say <strong class="font-semibold">“Deploy ready”</strong> and I’ll prepare everything. This thing is about to be on the fairway 24/7 for you and the crew — no server bills, no laptop needed.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">What’s your next shot? ⛳️</p></div></div><section class="inline-media-container flex flex-col gap-1 clear-both"></section></div><div class="order-first sticky hidden @md/mainview:block top-11 h-0 opacity-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100 -ml-[36px] @lg/mainview:-ml-[40px] -left-[26px]"><div class="min-h-7 py-4 flex flex-col gap-0.5"></div></div><div class="action-buttons h-8 mt-0.5 mb-2 flex flex-row flex-wrap w-full justify-between print:hidden"><div class="flex items-center gap-[2px] w-max rounded-lg text-xs px-2 start-0 @md/chat:start-3 -ml-4" style="bottom: 0px;"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium leading-[normal] cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-colors duration-100 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 select-none text-fg-secondary hover:text-fg-primary hover:bg-button-ghost-hover disabled:hover:text-fg-secondary disabled:hover:bg-transparent [&amp;_svg]:hover:text-fg-primary h-8 w-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100 [.last-response_&amp;]:opacity-100 disabled:opacity-0 group-focus-within:disabled:opacity-60 group-hover:disabled:opacity-60 [.last-response_&amp;]:disabled:opacity-60" type="button" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><div style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"><div class="[&amp;&gt;svg_*]:stroke-current" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); content-visibility: visible;"><defs><clippath id="__lottie_element_972"><rect width="24" height="24" x="0" y="0"></rect></clippath><g id="__lottie_element_