<h3 dir="auto" class="font-semibold text-xl max-md:font-display max-md:text-[19px] max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:tracking-[0px] max-md:mb-3 max-md:mt-3">Recommended Repository Description:</h3>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong class="font-semibold">"Fairway Friends - Free golf social network for posting rounds, scores, comments &amp; leaderboards. Built for the crew."</strong></p>
<h3 dir="auto" class="font-semibold text-xl max-md:font-display max-md:text-[19px] max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:tracking-[0px] max-md:mb-3 max-md:mt-3">Alternative Versions (pick whichever you like):</h3>
<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">"A free golf social app where friends post rounds, track scores, chat, and compete on leaderboards."</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">"Golf Social Network: Share your rounds, compare scores, and keep the banter going with your golf crew."</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">"Fairway Friends ⛳️ – Post rounds, leaderboards, comments. Free &amp; open for local golfers."</li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Just paste one into the <strong class="font-semibold">Description</strong> box when creating the repo.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Once it’s created, tell me and I’ll walk you through uploading the files and going live in under 2 minutes.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Ready for the next step? What's the repo name you're using?</p></div></div><section class="inline-media-container flex flex-col gap-1 clear-both"></section></div><div class="order-first sticky hidden @md/mainview:block top-11 h-0 opacity-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100 -ml-[36px] @lg/mainview:-ml-[40px] -left-[26px]"><div class="min-h-7 py-4 flex flex-col gap-0.5"></div></div><div class="action-buttons h-8 mt-0.5 mb-2 flex flex-row flex-wrap w-full justify-between print:hidden"><div class="flex items-center gap-[2px] w-max rounded-lg text-xs px-2 start-0 @md/chat:start-3 -ml-4" style="bottom: 0px;"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium leading-[normal] cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-colors duration-100 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 select-none text-fg-secondary hover:text-fg-primary hover:bg-button-ghost-hover disabled:hover:text-fg-secondary disabled:hover:bg-transparent [&amp;_svg]:hover:text-fg-primary h-8 w-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100 [.last-response_&amp;]:opacity-100 disabled:opacity-0 group-focus-within:disabled:opacity-60 group-hover:disabled:opacity-60 [.last-response_&amp;]:disabled:opacity-60" type="button" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><div style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"><div class="[&amp;&gt;svg_*]:stroke-current" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); content-visibility: visible;"><defs><clippath id="__lottie_element_1572"><rect width="24" height="24" x="0" y="0"></rect>