<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Repo <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300">fairway-friends</span> is created — now let’s get it live.</p>
<h3 dir="auto" class="font-semibold text-xl max-md:font-display max-md:text-[19px] max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:tracking-[0px] max-md:mb-3 max-md:mt-3">Step-by-Step (takes ~2 minutes):</h3>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><strong class="font-semibold">Upload the Files</strong><ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Go to your repo: <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300">github.com/yourusername/fairway-friends</span></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Click the big green <strong class="font-semibold">"Add file"</strong> → <strong class="font-semibold">"Upload files"</strong></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Drag and drop these three files:<ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><button class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono cursor-pointer bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300" type="button">index.html</button></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><button class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono cursor-pointer bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300" type="button">styles.css</button></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><button class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono cursor-pointer bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300" type="button">script.js</button></li>
</ul></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Add a commit message like “Initial upload”</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Click <strong class="font-semibold">"Commit changes"</strong></li>
</ul></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><strong class="font-semibold">Turn on GitHub Pages</strong><ul dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Click <strong class="font-semibold">Settings</strong> tab (top right)</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Scroll down to <strong class="font-semibold">Pages</strong> (left sidebar)</li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Under “Source”, choose <strong class="font-semibold">Deploy from a branch</strong></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Select <strong class="font-semibold">main</strong> branch → Click <strong class="font-semibold">Save</strong></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal">Wait ~30-60 seconds</li>
</ul></li>
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal"><strong class="font-semibold">Your Live Site</strong>
Refresh the Pages settings — you’ll see a link like:
<span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-300">https://yourusername.github.io/fairway-friends</span></li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong class="font-semibold">Go visit that link</strong> once it’s ready — your site should be online!</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Let me know when you’ve done step 1 (files uploaded) or if you hit any snag, and I’ll guide the rest or fix anything needed.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">We’re about to have <strong class="font-semibold">Fairway Friends</strong> live for the crew — super exciting! ⛳️🚀</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">What’s your status?</p></div></div><section class="inline-media-container flex flex-col gap-1 clear-both"></section></div><div class="order-first sticky hidden @md/mainview:block top-11 h-0 opacity-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100 -ml-[36px] @lg/mainview:-ml-[40px] -left-[26px]"><div class="min-h-7 py-4 flex flex-col gap-0.5"></div></div><div class="action-buttons h-8 mt-0.5 mb-2 flex flex-row flex-wrap w-full justify-between print:hidden"><div class="flex items-center gap-[2px] w-max rounded-lg text-xs px-2 start-0 @md/chat:start-3 -ml-4" style="bottom: 0px;"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium leading-[normal] cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-colors duration-100 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 select-none text-fg-secondary hover:text-fg-primary hover:bg-button-ghost-hover disabled:hover:text-fg-secondary disabled:hover:bg-transparent [&amp;_svg]:hover:text-fg-primary h-8 w-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100 [.last-response_&amp;]:opacity-100 disabled:opacity-0 group-focus-within:disabled:opacity-60 group-hover:disabled:opacity-60 [.last-response_&amp;]:disabled:opacity-60" type="button" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><div style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"><div class="[&amp;&gt;svg_*]:stroke-current" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); content-visibility: visible;"><defs><clippath id="__lottie_element_1761"><rect width="24" height="24" x="0" y="0"></rect></clippath><g id="__lottie_element_1768"