<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Take your time uploading the files. Once they're in and you've enabled GitHub Pages, drop the live link here and I'll check it out + give you any quick tweaks if needed.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">If you run into any hiccup (like the site not showing right or files not uploading), just paste what you're seeing and I'll help immediately.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words last:mb-0 max-md:leading-[155%] max-md:mb-4 max-md:last:mb-0" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Almost there — your free golf social network is about to be live 24/7 for you and the crew.</p>
