 as if addressing a professional colleague.\",\"description\":\"Responds using a formal tone.\",\"isPreset\":true},{\"personalityId\":\"tutor\",\"name\":\"Tutor\",\"prompt\":\"Respond as a Socratic teacher, guiding the user through questions and reasoning to foster deep understanding. Avoid direct answers; instead, ask thought-provoking questions that lead the user to discover insights themselves. Prioritize clarity, curiosity, and learning, while remaining patient and encouraging.\",\"description\":\"Responds in a way to help you learn.\",\"isPreset\":true},{\"personalityId\":\"comprehensive\",\"name\":\"Comprehensive\",\"prompt\":\"Provide thorough, detailed responses that explore topics from multiple angles. Include relevant context, examples, nuances, and implications. Structure information clearly with appropriate depth, covering edge cases and related considerations. Aim for completeness while maintaining clarity and organization.\",\"description\":\"Responds with thorough explanations.\",\"isPreset\":true}]},\"voice_mode_config\":{},\"max_files\":{\"max_files\":100},\"is_xai_employee\":false,\"is_x_employee\":false,\"new_voice_mode_1.0.36\":false,\"voice_mode_camera_rollout\":false,\"gork_voice_rollout\":false,\"allow_custom_prompts\":false,\"grok_4_mini_enable_inline_charts\":true,\"fast_followup_config\":{\"enabled\":false},\"tool_composer_config\":{\"max_qps_per_tool\":100,\"server_rate_limit_config\":{\"default\":100},\"client_rate_limit_config\":{\"default\":{\"default\":100}}},\"satisfaction_score\":3,\"mixpanel_server_url\":\"\",\"try_projects_name\":\"pick-personas\",\"grok_code_install_command\":\"npm install -g @xai-official/grok\",\"grok_mode_extras\":{\"extra_modes\":[\"grok-420\"]},\"supergrok_subscriptions\":{\"groupID\":\"21630009\",\"subscriptions\":[{\"id\":\"grok.pro.monthly.30\",\"title\":\"Imagine 1.0 is here – our best image \u0026 video experience yet\",\"trialSubscribeText\":\"\",\"subscribeText\":\"\",\"priceDetails\":\"\",\"tier\":\"grokPro\",\"benefits\":{\"header\":\"\",\"list\":[\"Longer conversations in Chat\",\"Higher usage on Grok Imagine 1.0\",\"Higher usage on Voice Mode and Companions\",\"Early access to new features\"],\"items\":[{\"customIcon\":\"grok-star\",\"title\":\"Longer conversations in Chat\"},{\"customIcon\":\"grok-make-image\",\"title\":\"Higher usage on Grok Imagine 1.0\"},{\"customIcon\":\"grok-waveform\",\"title\":\"Higher usage on Voice Mode and Companions\"},{\"customIcon\":\"grok-thumbs-up\",\"title\":\"Early access to new features\"}]}},{\"id\":\"supergrok.pro.monthly.300\",\"title\":\"Imagine 1.0 is here – our best image \u0026 video experience yet\",\"subscribeText\":\"\",\"priceDetails\":\"\",\"tier\":\"superGrokPro\",\"trialSubscribeText\":\"\",\"benefits\":{\"header\":\"\",\"list\":[],\"items\":[]}}]},\"enable_memory_v2_explicit_tools\":false,\"grok_build_symbol_references\":true,\"subscriptions_supergroklite_backend_enabled\":false,\"enable_user_custom_skills\":true,\"subscriptions_supergroklite_backend_android_enabled\":false,\"enable_file_upload_v2\":false,\"opal-marmot\":false,\"user_shard\":\"shard_1\",\"v2_direct_upload_max_size_mb\":10,\"web_file_upload\":{\"v2_enabled\":true,\"v2_direct_upload_max_size_mb\":16,\"is_direct_to_http\":true,\"max_upload_file_size_mb\":150,\"max_upload_video_size_mb\":150,\"multipart_supported\":true,\"multipart_concurrency\":4},\"imagine-caption-presets-v2\":{\"Standard\":{\"preset\":\"default\",\"previewImageUrl\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/grok-web-public/imagine-caption-presets/caption-standard.png\"},\"Colored\":{\"preset\":\"standout\",\"previewImageUrl\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/grok-web-public/imagine-caption-presets/caption-colored.png\"},\"Highlight\":{\"preset\":\"lively\",\"previewImageUrl\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/grok-web-public/imagine-caption-presets/caption-highlight.png\"}},\"voice_agent_builder_cta_config\":{\"enabled\":false,\"redirectURL\":\"https://x.ai/voice\",\"opensInExternalBrow